content: Loved the story and puzzles but the game was rather short plus there isn't a bonus chapter either.
Changed to 5 stars. Very imaginative game. Great puzzles and graphics

Brilliant! I've long been a fan of Artifex Mundi and this game doesn't disappoint. Love the storyline, no silly cutesie creatures and great puzzles. 5 stars also to the voice over artists, one of my pet hates is terrible acting on the vo totally ruining the game.
Another great game by Artifex. The story is great, with nice Italian scenery and roman mythology.
Display is not good, the hint button and other stuff are hidden. I have enjoyed all the other games but can't play this one due to this issue.

This game has an amazing story line with puzzles that are obvious but not to, to easy.. Not to many HO segments . (Less is more IMHO) I have to say that I'm loving this game so far!! I highly reccomend it !! Kudos to all those involved in the making of The Myst Seekers it's great and you did a amazing job. BUY it you won't regret it!!
Story is fun, graphics are well done, map is helpful , GOOD job!
Resolution and display issues for Galaxy S10+ Hint button and any items above it are off screen.
Over all it is a good game and the story line is pretty good, my only make against it would be the ending. The ending could have been done better. Off to play the second one ;)
s a very good game. ive played it before and my purchase was restored. love that
Enjoyed  the game.  Would have liked a bonus.
Great story good play but No bonus game
